flowchart TB
  REQ[Reverse geocode request] --> CACHE{Cache hit?}
  CACHE -- yes --> RES[Return cached]
  CACHE -- no --> RL[Rate limiter]
  RL --> TRY[Call Nominatim\n(timeout + retry)]
  TRY --> OK{Response OK?}
  OK -- yes --> SAVE[Store cache]
  SAVE --> RES
  OK -- no --> DEG[Degraded mode\nraw coords + low confidence]
  DEG --> RES
